00:14:16,472 --> 00:14:19,572
Come to think of it, she appeared a little bit

278
00:14:19,572 --> 00:14:21,972
during the final scene of the drama.

279
00:14:26,845 --> 00:14:28,372
See, it's this girl!

280
00:14:28,372 --> 00:14:30,849
Thank you, Masked Baiya!

281
00:14:30,849 --> 00:14:33,972
Cute!

282
00:14:33,972 --> 00:14:36,855
She is, isn't she? Her name was Naeko Miike

283
00:14:36,855 --> 00:14:39,372
and she was really popular among the boys in class.

284
00:14:39,372 --> 00:14:40,572
But...

285
00:14:40,572 --> 00:14:41,572
Nothing...

286
00:14:41,572 --> 00:14:44,072
To think that a girl who looks like an idol like this

287
00:14:44,072 --> 00:14:46,372
would fall in love you, Officer Chiba.

288
00:14:46,372 --> 00:14:47,472
Hey, hey...

289
00:14:47,472 --> 00:14:49,672
Did she really like you?

290
00:14:49,672 --> 00:14:51,272
Do you have any recollection

291
00:14:51,272 --> 00:14:53,572
of having done something to make her like you?

292
00:14:53,572 --> 00:14:57,472
The thing is, I have no such recollection.

293
00:14:57,472 --> 00:15:00,472
I did make her cry just once though.

294
00:15:00,472 --> 00:15:01,672
Were you mean to her?

295
00:15:01,672 --> 00:15:02,872
How dare you!

296
00:15:02,872 --> 00:15:05,272
No, I wasn't mean or anything,

297
00:15:05,272 --> 00:15:06,872
she just suddenly started crying.

298
00:15:06,872 --> 00:15:08,472
If I remember correctly,

299
00:15:08,472 --> 00:15:09,872
we went home a bit late

300
00:15:09,872 --> 00:15:12,372
because of things that we had to do at the broadcast club.

301
00:15:12,372 --> 00:15:15,272
When we got to the crosswalk, she suddenly started to cry.

302
00:15:17,472 --> 00:15:20,672
