00:23:15,372 --> 00:23:17,072
What?

446
00:23:17,072 --> 00:23:18,372
You were brushed off?

447
00:23:18,372 --> 00:23:21,772
Yeah. Well, I guess so.

448
00:23:21,772 --> 00:23:22,972
No joke.

449
00:23:22,972 --> 00:23:25,772
I guess she was too high on the pedestal after all.

450
00:23:25,772 --> 00:23:28,372
-Hey... -What're you doing?

451
00:23:28,372 --> 00:23:30,572
We'll resume investigations.

452
00:23:30,572 --> 00:23:32,272
Yes, sir.

453
00:23:32,272 --> 00:23:34,372
This is a secret, all right?

454
00:23:34,372 --> 00:23:35,872
Okay...

455
00:23:36,972 --> 00:23:38,872
That's good to hear.

456
00:23:38,872 --> 00:23:40,472
I'm going to tell Miwako about it.

457
00:23:40,472 --> 00:23:41,772
About that...

458
00:23:41,772 --> 00:23:44,072
If he was brushed off,

459
00:23:44,072 --> 00:23:45,972
